HEADWORD: Eastwards
<hw>East"wards</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>adv.</pos> <def>Toward the east; in the
direction of east from some point or place; <as>as, New Haven lies
<ex>eastward</ex> from New York</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

